            "headline": "COLDRIVER group presents new malware LOSTKEYS to steal from Western targets, Google report states. Company takes steps to mitigate any damage caused by the malware. LOSTKEYS is capable of stealing files and sending system information back to COLDRIVER. Losses from crypto hacks reach $2 billion in Q1 2025, surpassing total losses for 2024. Hacken report highlights operational flaws and social engineering tactics as key vulnerabilities. Bybit exchange suffers $1.5 billion hack orchestrated by Lazarus Group.",
